{"id":5279,"date":"2026-01-16T07:52:13","date_gmt":"2026-01-16T07:52:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/?p=5279"},"modified":"2026-01-17T03:06:50","modified_gmt":"2026-01-17T03:06:50","slug":"hot-filling-machine","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/hot-filling-machine.html","title":{"rendered":"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This artical we talk and discuss about the hot filling machine from its technology, construcion materials and Industrial Applications.It will help users to understand the hot filling and know how to choose a hot filling machine for their products.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is a hot filling machine?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A hot filling machine is type of filling and dosing equipment designed to fill liquids or semi-liquids into containers while the product is still heated. This work process is typically used for two main reasons: either to make the products easier to flow by heating it until it melts into liquid, or to ensure the product is sterile for longer shelf life. You\u2019ll find hot filling machines commonly used for products like juices, sauce,butter or some type of honey, which require heat to prevent spoilage. They\u2019re also essential for products such as candles, lip balms, lipstick,car wax, and petroleum-based goods, such as grease, also some chemicals, such as glue.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hot Filling Technology<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Npack has been in construction filling machines for more than 15 years, we conclude the hot filling technology mainly used in two different ways, depending on whether the product is liquid or semi-solid.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>1. Heat-for-Safety Filling (for liquids)<\/strong><br>This is the standard path for drinks, sauces, and similar food products. The goal is to sterilize and kill germs of the liquid and for a long shelf life without needing preservatives. The working process uses a powerful one-two punch: first, the liquid is sterilized at very high temperatures normally from 135\u00b0C to150\u00b0C to kill germs, and then it&#8217;s filled into containers while still piping hot(85\u201396\u00b0C). As it cools, it creates a vacuum seal, locking in safety and freshness. You&#8217;ll find this used for everything from bottled juices and iced tea to pasta sauces and drinkable yogurts. For food indusry , this technology is the most popular way. we can call this technology as thermal Sterilization Filling.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>2. Heat-to-Fill Filling (for semi-solids)<\/strong><br>This way is for products that are solid at room temperature but must be melted when filling and package. Heating is used to carefully turn the product into a thick, pourable fluid liquid. Once filled into its final packaging containers (such as a lipstick tube or a grease cartridge), it cools back into its familiar solid form. This is essential for products like lipsticks, deodorants, petroleum jelly, industrial greases, and solid perfumes. we can call this technology as Melt-Phase Filling.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">While these heating filling systems solve different issues, they share one non-negotiable requirement:&nbsp;extremely precise control of temperature<strong>.<\/strong>&nbsp;Every step depends on getting the heat just right.<\/p>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-advancedgallery .kb-gallery-type-grid.kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a{margin:-5px;}.kb-gallery-type-grid.kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a .kadence-blocks-gallery-item{padding:5px;}.kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a .kadence-blocks-gallery-item .kb-gal-image-radius, .kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a .kb-slide-item .kb-gal-image-radius img{border-radius:0px 0px 0px 0px;;}.kb-gallery-caption-style-bottom.kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a .kadence-blocks-gallery-item .kadence-blocks-gallery-item-inner .kadence-blocks-gallery-item__caption, .kb-gallery-caption-style-bottom-hover.kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a .kadence-blocks-gallery-item .kadence-blocks-gallery-item-inner .kadence-blocks-gallery-item__caption{background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%);}<\/style><div class=\"kb-gallery-wrap-id-5279_13b524-0a alignnone wp-block-kadence-advancedgallery\"><ul class=\"kb-gallery-ul kb-gallery-non-static kb-gallery-type-grid kb-gallery-id-5279_13b524-0a kb-gallery-caption-style-bottom-hover kb-gallery-filter-none\" data-image-filter=\"none\" data-item-selector=\".kadence-blocks-gallery-item\" data-lightbox-caption=\"true\" data-columns-xxl=\"3\" data-columns-xl=\"3\" data-columns-md=\"3\" data-columns-sm=\"2\" data-columns-xs=\"1\" data-columns-ss=\"1\"><li class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item-inner\"><figure class=\"kb-gallery-figure kadence-blocks-gallery-item-has-caption\"><div class=\"kb-gal-image-radius\"><div class=\"kb-gallery-image-contain kadence-blocks-gallery-intrinsic kb-gallery-image-ratio-land32 kb-has-image-ratio-land32\" ><img alt=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" title=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082.webp\" width=\"1247\" height=\"831\" alt=\"lipstick filling machine\" data-full-image=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082.webp\" data-light-image=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082.webp\" data-id=\"5068\" class=\"wp-image-5068\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082.webp 1247w, https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082-18x12.webp 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1247px) 100vw, 1247px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item__caption\">lipstick filling machine<\/div><\/div><\/figure><\/div><\/li><li class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item-inner\"><figure class=\"kb-gallery-figure kadence-blocks-gallery-item-has-caption\"><div class=\"kb-gal-image-radius\"><div class=\"kb-gallery-image-contain kadence-blocks-gallery-intrinsic kb-gallery-image-ratio-land32 kb-has-image-ratio-land32\" ><img alt=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" title=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509451666.webp\" width=\"1300\" height=\"840\" alt=\"oil filling solutiuon\" data-full-image=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509451666.webp\" data-light-image=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509451666.webp\" data-id=\"5033\" class=\"wp-image-5033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509451666.webp 1300w, https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509451666-18x12.webp 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item__caption\">oil filling solutiuon<\/div><\/div><\/figure><\/div><\/li><li class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item-inner\"><figure class=\"kb-gallery-figure kadence-blocks-gallery-item-has-caption\"><div class=\"kb-gal-image-radius\"><div class=\"kb-gallery-image-contain kadence-blocks-gallery-intrinsic kb-gallery-image-ratio-land32 kb-has-image-ratio-land32\" ><img alt=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" title=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509395827.webp\" width=\"1300\" height=\"867\" alt=\"cosmetics filling machine\" data-full-image=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509395827.webp\" data-light-image=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509395827.webp\" data-id=\"5030\" class=\"wp-image-5030\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509395827.webp 1300w, https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121509395827-18x12.webp 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"kadence-blocks-gallery-item__caption\">cosmetics filling machine<\/div><\/div><\/figure><\/div><\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hot Filling Machine Construction Material<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Hot filling involves packing liquids at high temperatures (normally between 60\u00b0C and 140\u00b0C). So the materials that touch the liquid must be carefully chosen to ensure safety, durability, and hygiene. Npack strictly choose the material not only to meet the GMP, FDA, and also durability working in high temperature.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">316L Stainless Steel is one of the most common, reliable, and recommended choice for most food drink and cosmetics products.and the surface of treatment of the liquid contact parts are also important, such as electropolished&nbsp;finish;The seals and gaskets, we normally choose the PTFE \/ PFA&nbsp;,FKM \/ Viton and EPDM Rubber according to the liquid and product feature. A ceramic piston and valve is also one of the good choice for a cosmetics and pharmaceuticals liquid.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hot Filling Machine industry application<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Hot filling machines are used in many industries to package products that needs sterlization and solid at room temperature.It is mostly application in the cosmetics , phamarceuticals and food industry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In food industry, the hot filling is more applicaiton for the drinks and sauce, one is for sterilization and anther one is for long life keep.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In&nbsp;cosmetics, like for packing filling lipstick and lip gloss ,  when filling, mostly these products are in hot stage, for it is more easy to fill and after filling then cooling into its nature solid form.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hot Filling Machine Selection<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">there are many types of hot filling machines, here we select some equipments for you according to its filling technology, no matter which types, we have solutions for your hot filling needs.<\/p>\n\n\n<style>.kt-tabs-id5279_a0af70-62 > .kt-tabs-content-wrap > .wp-block-kadence-tab{border-top:3px solid #0a6689;border-right:0px solid #0a6689;border-bottom:0px solid #0a6689;border-left:0px solid #0a6689;border-top-left-radius:0px;border-top-right-radius:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;padding-top:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);padding-right:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);padding-bottom:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);padding-left:var(--global-kb-spacing-sm, 1.5rem);background:var(--global-palette9, #ffffff);}.wp-block-kadence-tabs .kt-tabs-id5279_a0af70-62 > .kt-tabs-title-list li{margin-top:0px;margin-right:8px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-tabs .kt-tabs-id5279_a0af70-62 > .kt-tabs-title-list li:last-child{margin-right:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-tabs .kt-tabs-id5279_a0af70-62 > .kt-tabs-title-list li .kt-tab-title, .wp-block-kadence-tabs .kt-tabs-id5279_a0af70-62 > .kt-tabs-content-wrap > .kt-tabs-accordion-title .kt-tab-title{line-height:1.4em;font-weight:regular;font-style:normal;border-top-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-le