ry.The hopper is with heating , mixing system, double jacket design, some are 3 layers jacket for  protection.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-tab kt-tab-inner-content kt-inner-tab-2 kt-inner-tab5279_b1235a-b7\"><div class=\"kt-tab-inner-content-inner\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/lipstick-filling-machine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\" noreferrer noopener\"><img alt=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" title=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1247\" height=\"831\" src=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082.webp\" alt=\"lipstick filling machine\" class=\"wp-image-5068 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082.webp 1247w, https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025121904403082-18x12.webp 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1247px) 100vw, 1247px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">For lipstick, deorant and other types of cosmetics and personal care products filling.Hot filling machine is one of the best choice for cosmetics products\u2014whether you\u2019re handling lipstick waxes or gooey deodorant melts\u2014is all about temperature management.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-tab kt-tab-inner-content kt-inner-tab-3 kt-inner-tab5279_5f6bac-46\"><div class=\"kt-tab-inner-content-inner\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img alt=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" title=\"Complete Guide to Hot Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1135\" height=\"865\" src=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2025111212072736.webp\" alt=\"BIB sauce filling machine\" class=\"wp-image-4384 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2025111212072736.webp 1135w, https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2025111212072736-16x12.webp 16w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1135px) 100vw, 1135px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A hot filling solution for greese, butter from 10g to 30KG, according to the accuracy and filling quantity, we offer different types of dosing system<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion: The Converging Future of Hot Filling Technologies<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">At its heart, The hot filling is about harnessing thermal energy to transform materials\u2014whether killing bacteria in juice or shaping lipstick. As products become more complex and consumer demands more exacting, mastering these technologies will be the key to staying competitive.Npack offers different types of filling machine for your hot filling requirements, please feel free to contact us if you have any enquiry.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This artical we talk and discuss about the hot filling machine from its technology, construcion materials and Industrial Applications.It will help users to understand the hot filling and know how to choose a hot filling machine for their products. What is a hot filling machine? A hot filling machine is type of filling and dosing [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3721,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[36],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5279","post","type-post","status-pub